  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <article class="person">
      <img src="/images/rohit.jpg" alt="Rohit Sharma" class="portrait">
      
      <h1>Rohit Sharma</h1>
      <p class="player-meta"><strong>Role:</strong> Opening Batter (Right-handed) & Captain</p>
      <p class="player-bio">Rohit Sharma is a stylish opening batsman renowned for his ability to dominate bowling attacks with elegant strokeplay. Known as the "Hitman" for his explosive batting, he holds multiple world records and has been instrumental in India's success in limited-overs cricket.</p>

      <section>
        <h3>Playing Style & Strengths</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Batting Style:</strong> Right-handed opener with elegant technique</li>
          <li><strong>Signature Strength:</strong> Big hundreds and powerful six-hitting ability</li>
          <li><strong>Format Expertise:</strong> Exceptionally successful in limited-overs formats</li>
          <li><strong>Notable Quality:</strong> Record holder for highest individual ODI score (264)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>Career Highlights</h3>
        <div class="stats-grid">
